Introduction

Yoo Taeyang is the lead vocalist and main dancer of the boy group SF9 under FNC Entertainment. Aside from singing and dancing, Taeyang is also good at playing the guitar and calligraphy.

He debuted as a member of SF9 on October 5, 2016, with the group's first single album "Feeling Sensation".
